description: JUST LISTED IN THE GUARD GATED COMMUNITY OF SEACLIFF ON THE GREENS!  This 500 model has a desirable corner lot.  Extremely light and bright  with 2298 square feet of living space with 2.5 baths, 2 full bedrooms + loft area and a office.  Master Bedroom has vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet and a separate wardrobe closet. Master bath has just been remodeled with soaking tub, dual sinks and vanity and wall in shower. The other bathrooms are also redone. Central vacuum, shutters thru out and updated window and sliders. There is a sound system thru out home and also on patio.  There is a spacious two car garage with lots of build-in cabinets.  Close proximity to the beach, Pacific City and restaurants.  Within walking distance to The Huntington Club, golf and tennis.  THIS ONE WON'T LAST!!

description: This home is ideal for those who appreciate modern amenities and thoughtful design. With plenty of space to spread out, it's a perfect place to call home. First flr features convenient laundry room, perfect for busy lifestyles, as well as an office, ideal for those who work from home. The dining room is perfect for entertaining guests, while the finished basement provides plenty of additional space for rec or relaxation. The keeping room, adorned with shiplap walls,  is a comfortable space to gather with loved ones, while the family room, central to the home, is complete w/fireplace for chilly evenings. Make your way upstairs to find 2 additional bedrooms offering plenty of space. Both share access to a full bath that has been tastefully updated. The Master Suite includes a walk-in closet and modern en suite full bath. But the real showstopper is the gorgeous inground pool, perfect for enjoying warm weather & outdoor activities. Imagine spending weekends lounging poolside, simply enjoying the peaceful tranquility of your own backyard oasis. This home truly has it all. Don't miss opportunity to live in the home of your dreams! Delay Show 3/17 10AM; Delay Negotiation 3/21 4PM.

description: Welcome to paradise! Caicos Model Villa home in the award-winning Latitude Margaritaville resort style community in the heart of beautiful Daytona Beach, FL.  This well appointed 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom with den Villa features upgrades throughout and includes an open floor plan, spacious kitchen with 42-inch uppers, under cabinet lighting, custom tile backsplash, 9 foot ceilings throughout, high efficiency heating & air, screened in lanai and more.   Latitude Margaritaville is a place where life rolls easy, neighbors are friends, and the party never ends. Awesome recreation, dining and entertainment will make the town center the place to be. You’ve earned a life where every day feels like an escape. Find your paradise at the 55-and-better community where fun and relaxation meet. Escape to Jimmy Buffet's island-inspired living as you grow older, but not up. Top of the line amenities include the private Bar & Chill restaurant, resort style pool, Fins-Up Fitness Center, Outdoor Band Shell, Last Mango Theater, Work & Play Center, Dog Park and Pet Spa, Fitness Trails, Pickleball, Bocce Ball, Tennis Courts, Basketball Courts along with the Private Beach Club. Golf cart community with paths to the Latitude Landing which includes a grocery store,  restaurants, several retail outlets including insurance, hair salon, nail salon, pet boutique, and more. description: Do not miss out on this 2 bedroom, 2 full bathroom condo in Park North at Cheney located in Orlando. The unit has plenty of natural light coming in from the windows and balcony double doors. With a view straight out to the pool area, you won’t even realize you’re downtown. And you can enjoy that view right from your balcony. The condo opens straight into your kitchen and living areas: open and perfect for entertaining. The dining area easily accommodates a full-size dining room table; allowing you plenty of room for guests or formal dinners. The guest bathroom has been tastefully updated, and both bedrooms feature large walk-in closets. The split floor plan features a large primary bedroom toward the rear of the unit, with a large en-suite bathroom, including a soaker tub. And the HVAC (including the air handler and the condenser), refrigerator, microwave and dishwasher were all updated in the last year.  Park North at Cheney place has 2 gorgeous pools, 3 elevators, fitness centers, a business center, laundry, and a very large common area. Fee includes water, sewer, trash collection and reserves. And the location is adjacent to restaurants, shopping and highways.

description: Beautiful vinyl sided ''Classic 2-Story'' with in-ground swimming pool! Welcoming wrap-around front porch with columns is partially screened-in. You'll love the gorgeous front entry with oak staircase and the many rooms with ornate woodwork & hardwood flooring! Newer kitchen with granite countertops, snack bar, stainless appliances & pantry cupboard. Sitting room off of the formal dining room. Spacious 15x23 living room with fireplace. Open stairway to 2nd floor landing, 3 bedrooms plus nursery, remodeled bath. Large walk-in closet off primary BR. Finished basement area includes family room, 4th bedroom w/egress, laundry & newer full bath. Pool area features a deck with pergola & beautiful landscaping. Excellent south village location.  View this truly one-of-a-kind historical home today!

description:
LIFE SIMPLIFIED
Take a look at this beautiful home featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and approximately 1,936 square feet. Enjoy the freedom of a virtually maintenance free lifestyle while residing in a great community. This home is professionally managed and maintained by Tricon American Homes. You deserve single family rental living at its best!
BEWARE OF LEASING FRAUD! If you believe someone else is trying to rent you this home or have any questions regarding leasing fraud, please call our Fraud Prevention Hotline at 877.241.

Completed applications approved on "first-come, first-served" basis.

 - Non-refundable application fee: $49.99 per occupant of age 18 or older
 - One-year or longer lease minimum
 - Non-refundable holding fee: $250 per home, credited to approved applicant's first month's rent after move in
 - Utilities: Resident pays for all utilities including trash, sewer,and water
 - Animals approved with pet fee and monthly animal rent
 - Breed Restrictions: American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, Bull Mastiff, Chow, Doberman, Pit Bull, Presa Canario, Rottweiler, Wolf, Wolf hybrids, any combination mix of the foregoing breeds, and any other breed or type that Landlord deems to have similar characteristics.
 - Pets: Maximum two animals allowed. Acceptable types of pets include dogs, cats, birds, small caged mammals, and fish. Livestock, farm animals, and poisonous, dangerous, or exotic animals are prohibited.
 - Equal Housing Opportunity
 - Pricing is subject to change without notice. Some pricing may include special offers based on lease terms and date of occupancy.
 - Security deposit varies based uponcredit criteria; however standard security deposit equals one month's rent.
 - Pool Maintenance Fee: $95 per month pool maintenance fee will be added to any home with a pool.
 - Approved Applicants are required to execute a Lease Agreement and submit the full security deposit within 48 hours after approval of the Lease. The Lease start date must be within 14 days after approval. This requirement is applicable to all Approved Applicants, even if they have not seen the inside of the home.
 - Smart Homes: Service available only on select homes. A monthly fee of $16.95 applies.

Please visit us atwww.TriconAmericanHomes.com
This home is part of an HOA, and may have additional rental qualifications and policies. Please consult with your Leasing Agent for more details

description: Contract Pending. No Open House this Sunday. This large architectural diamond is situated on two downtown city lots that will accommodate another home, garage (plans attached), or maybe use the corner as a great business location! Featuring all the modern amenities one could expect, with new Granite Counter Tops, Carpet, Wood Flooring, Siding, Gutters, Paint, and so much more! There are two additional unfinished rooms on the 3rd floor, so this could be a 7-Bedroom house. All the appliances come with the property.  * Extra lot can be sold separately at $79K but is now included in the price.  * All measurements approximate or from County Accessors web site.

description: Absolutely adorable updated 2-bedroom, 1 bath Ranch w/one-car garage under close to all area amenities!  Lush 3.2 pastoral acre lot w/fabulous garden space, a nature lover's marsh out back.  Easy one-floor living plus a wonderful enclosed porch & full basement.  Also features an eat-in kitchen & large living room, other pluses include a newer furnace and roof, wood stove in basement as secondary heat source. Zoned Residential/Business & recently used as a hair salon, so options are endless for a buyer who wants a primary, secondary or investment property within 10 minutes of Lake and Mt. Sunapee & all Sunapee Region attractions.  All appliances stay!

description: You can now own this fantastic home just in time for the Holidays! A beautifully maintained and updated 5 bedroom, 3 full bath home located in Tucson's desirable Rita Ranch community and in the heart of the highly-rated Vail Unified School District. The home has been modernly updated with gorgeous granite countertops throughout the kitchen and bathrooms, ceramic tile downstairs, painted solid wood cabinets, a gas fireplace for cold nights, a large lush backyard with a second-story balcony, covered patio and storage shed; we even said goodbye to the gold and added modern chrome hardware and lighting. The Owners have been meticulous about the care of this home and now it's time for you to enjoy. Come see it for yourself!

description: Classic 4 BR 3Ba W/O nestled on a pretty treed lot just 3 blocks to the East entrance to Hyland Park Preserve.  A 2012 remodel of the kitchen with all new cabinets, granite counters and SS appliances is now open to the views from new windows which span the front of the house. Lots of options for entertaining and family fun in the walkout level with gas fireplace , perfect for cozy gatherings, as well as great space for an office or game area. Buyers will appreciate the heated garage on cold winter mornings,  its extra storage areas and walkout to a relaxing patio. Updates include a new roof in 2016, exterior painted and new windows on all except for the west side in 2018.
